{"id": "ChIJXTWiPHHDwoARZW5sk1ri81g", "rating": 3.7, "userRatingCount": 15, "displayName": {"text": "TSUKE Artisan Noodle", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJXTWiPHHDwoARZW5sk1ri81g/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25WWlIwcDFla2hYY0drNE5tUnFUamhGWjI5U2VHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I have been to plenty of ramen restaurants and have worked at many but in all my years nothing has come close to this. In all honesty the ramen broth is perfect and the karaage has actual seasonings and proper taste. The gyoza I was expecting frozen pan fried but these were massive and made by hand. The Chasu was next level. It was awesome and some of the best I’ve had. I was beyond full after this but I still got ramen to take home. 100/10 best ramen I’ve had. Talk about doing it right.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I have been to plenty of ramen restaurants and have worked at many but in all my years nothing has come close to this. In all honesty the ramen broth is perfect and the karaage has actual seasonings and proper taste. The gyoza I was expecting frozen pan fried but these were massive and made by hand. The Chasu was next level. It was awesome and some of the best I’ve had. I was beyond full after this but I still got ramen to take home. 100/10 best ramen I’ve had. Talk about doing it right.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "jonah martinez", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101759325235480724788/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIXwbdJJT2-9GTjLrRMSsXSYx9Bo3QQbj2D-1PIgsTMCQq-3w=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-05T18:44:04.835510900Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25WWlIwcDFla2hYY0drNE5tUnFUamhGWjI5U2VHYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRj